<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.7.8">
<l>eṉṉai nekiḻkkilu meṉṉuṭai naṉṉeñcan</l>
<l>taṉṉai yakalvikkat tāṉuṅkil lāṉiṉip</l>
<l>piṉṉai neṭumpaṇait tōḷmakiḻa pīṭuṭai</l>
<l>muṉṉai yamarar muḻumuta lāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>And if he were to cut me loose, even he himself</l>
<l>cannot make my good heart leave him now,</l>
<l>powerful when delighting in the large bamboo shoulders of Piṉṉai,</l>
<l>he who once was the whole base of the immortals.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
